lead_paragraph: Barcelona's poor run away to Real Sociedad continued when the champions were held to a 1-1 draw at Anoeta on Sunday and slipped six points behind La Liga leaders Real Madrid before next week's 'Clasico' against their arch rivals.

headline.print_headline: Barca Fall Six Points Behind Real Madrid After Draw at Real Sociedad
